  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "What is Dynamic Routing?"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Dynamic routing allows you to create routes with variable segments, enabling dynamic URLs like user profiles or product pages."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Basic Syntax"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "const routes = [\n  { path: '/user/:id', component: User }\n];"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Access Route Params"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "this.$route.params.id"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Template Example"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "html",
      "value": "<p>User ID: {{ $route.params.id }}</p>"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Multiple Params"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "{ path: '/user/:id/post/:postId', component: Post }"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Programmatic Navigation"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "this.$router.push({ path: `/user/${id}` });"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Named Routes with Params"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "this.$router.push({ name: 'user', params: { id: 1 } });"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Watching Route Changes"
    },
    {
      "type": "code",
      "language": "javascript",
      "value": "watch: {\n  '$route.params.id'(newId) {\n    // handle change\n  }\n}"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Use meaningful param names**",
        "**Validate route params**",
        "**Use named routes for navigation**",
        "**Watch route changes for updates**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Common Mistakes"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "value": [
        "**Not handling route param changes**",
        "**Incorrect param naming**",
        "**Using path instead of name incorrectly**",
        "**Not validating params**"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "value": "Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "value": "Dynamic routing is essential for building flexible Vue applications with dynamic URLs and content."
    }
  ],

